President Muhammadu Buhari is expected at the venue of the APC presidential rally in Lokoja, Kogi State any moment from now. Already, a mammoth crowd of APC members, supporters and leaders are gathered at the Lokoja Confluence Stadium, venue of the rally. Director General of Buhari/Osinbajo campaign organisation, Rotimi Amaechi, Minister of Internal Affairs, Abdulrahman Danbazzau and other top APC stalwarts from both the national and state levels are already on ground to receive the president. Osinbajo, Tinubu in Kogi as Audu concludes campaign Page 18 replacement Youths rally support for Buhari, Osinbajo re-election in Kogi